        "TileImage": "$($repository 856b2aa2-e224-48c3-b890-01fdf4dba6de).Image",
        "Description": "Good morning 47,Welcome to victor Creek.your target is Charles Blake III and Helen West.\r\rCharles pointed out several monopoly-style policies, all meant to keep power in his own hands, so he could make sure his underground drug and sex-trade operations ran smoothly.\r\rHelen helped him run his illegal drug operations and secretly handled the people who opposed him. Our client does not want these two villains to keep doing harm.\r\rGood Luck 47",
